Company Profile

China Hongyang Group is prospering rapidly and well-known by its dramatic inventions in the globe.

As a handcraft workshop founded in Wenzhou in 1992, Hongyang has been making great achievements in the international market and has become a comprehensive supplier in the field of Fuel Dispensers, Vapor Recovery unit, Online Monitoring Systems, CNG Dispensers, LNG Dispensers, L-CNG Skid-Mounted, LPG Dispensers, Gas Pressure Regulator, AdBule Dispenser, AC Electric Vehicle Chargers, DC Quick Electric Vehicle Chargers and Wireless Charging Systems.

From a manufacturer of single products to a diversified high-tech enterprise. Hongyang has gradually grown stronger and shipped their products to over 100 countries in Europe, South America, Southeast Asia, Middle East and Africa market.

Following high standards, Hongyang has obtained certifications issued by multiple countries and 22 authorized national patents. Has established its important position in the gas station equipment industry.

With a global vision, Hongyang insists on comprehensive fulfillment of the international strategy and gradually building global design, purchase, marketing and service networks with global competitiveness.

Shake hands with Hongyang! Share success together!
